metadata.name: #01: 'Lone Tree'
metadata.description:
From one corner of the world to the next. Beauty in mother nature can be discovered everywhere you look, especially in your own backyard.

This collection is the accumulation from the start of my creative career that are staples for my growth & vision. Each artwork is a piece of me and my creative journey.

In this collection, I wish to share some of my favourite photography & digital artworks I've created over the past 7 years.

Resolution 7500 x 5000px
